{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_45","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0`, but the failure appears to be after the Gradle lane was repaired, not in the final test execution itself. The first run failed in `compileTestJava` because `ChildReaper` and `Reaper` are not present in Curator 5.0.0 (`logs/org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-06T21-32-42-013155Z.log`). The next two JVM test runs then failed on missing ZooKeeper transitive classes, first `com.codahale.metrics.Reservoir` and then `org.xerial.snappy.SnappyInputStream` (`logs/org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-06T21-34-06-462105Z.log` and `logs/org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-06T21-34-44-947931Z.log`). After those fixes, later runs are green: `BUILD SUCCESSFUL` for `test`/`nativeTest` appears in `logs/org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-06T21-35-11-206427Z.log`, `logs/org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-06T21-36-28-586747Z.log`, and `logs/org.apache.curator:curator-recipes:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-06T21-36-49-718832Z.log`, and the generated reports show 6/6 JVM tests passing plus native JUnit passing.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-6695-fails-javac-compile-org.apache.curator-curator-recipes-5.0.0-8ca23530\n\nThe most likely failing stage is artifact/metrics finalization after a passing candidate. `stats/org.apache.curator/curator-recipes/5.0.0/execution-metrics.json` still records `status: \"failure\"`, `generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: \"None\"`, and `metadata_file: \"None\"`, while `metadata/org.apache.curator/curator-recipes/5.0.0/` is empty and `stats/org.apache.curator/curator-recipes/5.0.0/stats.json` was never written. The preserved candidate commit does contain real changes (test rewrite plus added `metrics-core` and `snappy-java` test dependencies), so the automation appears to have lost or skipped publishing the successful artifacts.\n\n1. Review the preserved branch and confirm the replacement of the removed `ChildReaper` coverage with `InterProcessMultiLock`, plus the added `metrics-core` and `snappy-java` test dependencies.\n2. Regenerate or publish the missing `metadata/org.apache.curator/curator-recipes/5.0.0/reachability-metadata.json` and `stats/org.apache.curator/curator-recipes/5.0.0/stats.json` from the passing candidate.\n3. Rerun the coordinate workflow once those artifacts are present to verify the metrics record flips from failure to success."}}
